      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRENTON'S ACE (8) is long overdue and boasts a solid record despite not having won her maiden yet, the latest finishing second at Ballarat. Has placed at her last two starts now. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Key chance in this line up. RITZY RUTH (4) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last four runs. Last start finished 2nd on March 18 over 425m at this track behind Space King beaten 0.8 lengths (24.58) in a Bottom Up - Maiden. Comes through a solid form race last start. Well-placed to take this out. HAVING A LOOK (1) broke from the inside draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only a neck (24.49) behind Land Of Anger at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from seven starts. Racing well and deserves a win. FRANKLY SPEED (2) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
